data.text: @FrogNews @MiamiDadeCounty Are we back to calling it the flu yet?

@FrogNews @MiamiDadeCounty time to finally do away with all the masking everywhere.  On the west coast for a week and never seen so many masks and refused to go into some because they wanted me to mask and take my temp.
@FrogNews @MiamiDadeCounty Those test kits & masks Biden sent out made all the difference in the world! Ended the Plague just like that! Now onto the next school play!
